---
title: Veggie Loaded Gnocchi with Red Pesto & Pine Nuts
description: These versatile Italian potato dumplings are beautiful baked, fried or boiled. In this recipe, we’ve pan fried them to give a lovely crispy edge which works perfectly with its creamy veg packed sauce. If you’re looking for a dish that will warm and nourish you from the inside out, then you’ve struck gold with this deliciously simple recipe.
